  <entry>
    <title>Tranquilpeak 테마 커스터마이징</title>
    <link href="https://cskime.github.io/2021/02/21/tranquilpeak-customizing/"/>
    <id>https://cskime.github.io/2021/02/21/tranquilpeak-customizing/</id>
    <published>2021-02-20T15:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-02-21T07:54:15.636Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Hexo의 tranquilpeak 테마를 사용하면서 <a href="https://github.com/LouisBarranqueiro/hexo-theme-tranquilpeak/blob/master/DOCUMENTATION.md">documentation</a>만 봐서는 어려웠던 커스터마이징 내용을 기록한다.</p><a id="more"></a><hr><!-- toc --><hr><h2 id="Utterances-comment"><a href="#Utterances-comment" class="headerlink" title="Utterances comment"></a>Utterances comment</h2><p><a href="https://utteranc.es/">Utterances</a>에서 configuration을 설정한 뒤 <strong>Enable Utterances</strong>에 생성된 script로 <code>themes/tranquilpeak/layout/_partial/post/utterances.ejs</code> 경로에 파일을 만든다.</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script src=<span class="string">&quot;https://utteranc.es/client.js&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        repo=<span class="string">&quot;&#123;username&#125;/&#123;repository&#125;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        issue-term=<span class="string">&quot;&#123;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        theme=<span class="string">&quot;github-light&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        crossorigin=<span class="string">&quot;anonymous&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">async</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>themes/tranquilpeak/_config.yml</code>에 utterances 사용을 위한 설정을 추가한다.</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># ---------------</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Comment systems</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># ---------------</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Utterances</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">utterances:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>themes/tranquilpeak/layout/_partial/post.ejs</code>에 utterances comment를 추가한다.</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;% <span class="keyword">if</span> (post.comments) &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% <span class="keyword">if</span> (theme.disqus_shortname) &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;%- partial(<span class="string">&#x27;post/disqus&#x27;</span>) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (theme.gitment.enable) &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;%- partial(<span class="string">&#x27;post/gitment&#x27;</span>) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (theme.gitalk.enable) &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;%- partial(<span class="string">&#x27;post/gitalk&#x27;</span>) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (theme.utterances.enable) &#123; %&gt; <span class="comment">// added</span></span><br><span class="line">        &lt;%- partial(<span class="string">&#x27;post/utterances&#x27;</span>) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% &#125; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;% &#125; %&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Font-변경"><a href="#Font-변경" class="headerlink" title="Font 변경"></a>Font 변경</h2><p>Tranquilpeak 테마에서 font를 변경하는 작업은 다음을 참고했다.</p><ul><li><a href="https://blog.weirdx.io/post/9016">Install Bower</a></li><li><a href="https://mingpd.github.io/2019/04/14/github-blog-with-hexo-1/#grunt">Chagne Font - grunt</a></li><li><a href="http://blog.lattecom.xyz/2016/05/08/tranquilpeak-theme-web-font/">Tranquilpeak theme web font</a></li></ul><div class="alert info"><p>Tranquilpeak 테마는 <code>.js</code> 및 <code>.css</code> 파일을 수정한 뒤 적용하려면 별도로 빌드를 해야 한다. 빌드를 위해 <code>bower</code>와 <code>grunt</code>를 설치한다.</p><figure class="highlight zsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install -g bower</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install -g grunt-cli</span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> themes/tranquilpeak</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install grunt --save-dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p><code>themes/tranquilpeak/source/_css/tranquilpeak.scss</code>에 web font를 import한다.</p><figure class="highlight scss"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">@import</span></span><br><span class="line">    url(<span class="attribute">http</span>://fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/notosanskr.css),</span><br><span class="line">    url(<span class="attribute">http</span>://fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/nanumgothiccoding.css);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>themes/tranquilpeak/source/_css/utils/_variables_.scss</code>에서 <strong>Font families</strong> 부분을 수정한다.</p><figure class="highlight scss"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Font families</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$open-sans</span>:            <span class="string">&#x27;Open Sans&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$open-sans-sans-serif</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;Open Sans&#x27;</span>, sans-serif;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$merriweather-serif</span>:   <span class="string">&#x27;Merriweather&#x27;</span>, serif;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$monospace</span>:             Menlo, Consolas, monospace;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$noto-sans-kr</span>:         <span class="string">&#x27;Noto Sans KR&#x27;</span>, sans-serif;          <span class="comment">// added</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$nanum-gothic-coding</span>:  <span class="string">&#x27;Nanum Gothic Coding&#x27;</span>, monospace;    <span class="comment">// added</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$font-family-base</span>: <span class="variable">$noto-sans-kr</span>;   <span class="comment">// open-sans-sans-serif;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$font-families</span>: (</span><br><span class="line">   // base</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">&#x27;headings&#x27;</span>:          <span class="variable">$noto-sans-kr</span>,   // open-sans-sans-serif,</span><br><span class="line">   // components</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">&#x27;code&#x27;</span>:              <span class="variable">$monospace</span>,</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">&#x27;caption&#x27;</span>:           <span class="variable">$noto-sans-kr</span>,   // merriweather-serif,</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">&#x27;image-gallery&#x27;</span>:     <span class="variable">$noto-sans-kr</span>,   // open-sans,</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">&#x27;post-header-cover&#x27;</span>: <span class="variable">$noto-sans-kr</span>,   // merriweather-serif,</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">&#x27;post-meta&#x27;</span>:         <span class="variable">$noto-sans-kr</span>,   // open-sans-sans-serif,</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">&#x27;post-content&#x27;</span>:      <span class="variable">$noto-sans-kr</span>,   // merriweather-serif,</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">&#x27;post-excerpt-link&#x27;</span>: <span class="variable">$noto-sans-kr</span>,   // open-sans-sans-serif,</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">&#x27;highlight&#x27;</span>:         <span class="variable">$monospace</span>,</span><br><span class="line">   // layout</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">&#x27;sidebar&#x27;</span>:           <span class="variable">$noto-sans-kr</span>   // open-sans-sans-serif</span><br><span class="line">);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>변경한 font를 적용하기 위해 <code>themes/tranquilpeak</code> 경로에서 아래 shell을 실행한다.</p><figure class="highlight zsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install</span><br><span class="line">$ bower install jquery</span><br><span class="line">$ grunt build</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Hexo의 tranquilpeak 테마를 사용하면서 &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/LouisBarranqueiro/hexo-theme-tranquilpeak/blob/master/DOCUMENTATION.md&quot;&gt;documentation&lt;/a&gt;만 봐서는 어려웠던 커스터마이징 내용을 기록한다.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
